  <num>28-3602</num>
  <heading>Finance charge.</heading>
  <text>Such a bank or savings and loan association may contract for and receive interest at the rate provided for in <cite path="subtitle|33" proof="true">Chapter 33 of this subtitle</cite>, or, in lieu of such interest, a finance charge which, if expressed as an annual percentage rate, does not exceed a rate of 21% per annum on the unpaid balances of principal.</text>
